      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the resistance thing but it feels so extreme to take them for 10 days when the skin is already totally clear. like, if a doctor sees a patient who is perfectly fine and the infection is gone, they'd probably be fine with stopping, right? i just want a straight answer on whether it's actually dangerous to stop now or if people just say that to be safe. can i just finish the ones i have left and call it a day?",
